All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AnimationThread
The Class AnimationThread is responsible for updating the view and updating the tangent pair.
ArrayListHull
The Class ArrayListHull represents a contour polygon or a convex hull.
CHGO_8493367_Kuhn_Manuel
The Class CHGO_8493367_Kuhn_Manuel contains the entry point of the program i.e. the public static void main(String[]) method.
CommandEvent
This event indicates that the user wants to undo a command that was previously executed, or wants to execute again a command that was previously undone.
CommandEventType
The Enum CommandEventType specifies the type of a command event.
CommandManager
The Class CommandManager is responsible for handling the commands for the redo and undo functionality of the GUI.
ContourType
The Enum ContourType identifies the 4 contours of the contour polygon i.e. the convex hull.
ConventionalParser
A Parser which can extract a point from a string.
Diameter
The Class Diameter represents the diameter of the convex hull which is a pair of two points A and B of the hull.
DiameterAndQuadrangleCalculator
The Class DiameterAndQuadrangleCalculator provides a calculator, which takes a convex hull as an argument and calculates the longest diameter and the quadrangle with maximum area.
DittmarTriangleCalculator
The Class TriangleCalculator calculates the biggest triangle of a convex hull.
DobkinTriangleCalculator
The Class TriangleCalculator calculates the biggest triangle of a convex hull.
DragPointCommand
The command for dragging a point from one position to another position.
DrawPanel
This Class represents the draw panel.
DrawPanelController
The controller of the draw panel.
DrawPanelEvent
The Class DrawPanelEvent specifies all events which are generated by the user on the draw panel.
DrawPanelEventType
The Enum DrawPanelEventType.
DrawPanelListener
The listener for receiving drawPanel events produced by the user by changing the point set or moving the mouse.
FileChooser
The Class FileChooser extends JFileChooser.
FileEvent
The Class FileEvent specifies an event generated by the user by creating a new file, by opening or saving a file or by exciting the application.
FileEventType
The Enum FileEventType specifies the type of a file event.
FileManager
The Class FileManager handles all tasks related to creating a new file, opening a file, saving a file and saving a file before terminating the program.
FileSettings
The Class FileSettings contains the default file paths for the file chooser and the operational manual.
GUISettings
The Class GUISettings contains the title of the application, the colors for the draw panel, the default settings for the menus, the radius of the displayed points, the radius of the mouse pointer and some information about the main window size.
HullCalculator
The Class HullCalculator implements IHullCalculator which is the test interface for this application.
ICommand
The Command Interface as used for the command pattern.
IDrawPanel
The Interface for the draw panel.
IDrawPanelController
The Interface for the draw panel controller.
IDrawPanelControllerObserver
The Interface for the observer of a draw panel controller.
IDrawPanelListener
The listener Interface for receiving drawPanel events produced by the user by inserting, deleting or dragging points or by moving the mouse.
IFileManager
The Interface for the file manager.
IHull
The Interface for a hull which can be the contour polygon and the convex hull.
IHullIterator
An Interface for an iterator, which allows the programmer to traverse the points of the hull in both directions.
IMainWindow
The Interface for the main window.
IMainWindowListener
The listener for receiving main window events.
IMetric
The Interface IMetric provides a method to measure the distance between two points.
InsertPointCommand
Command for inserting a point into the point set.
InsertRandomPointsCommand
Command for inserting a number of randomly generated points into a point set.
IParser
An Interface for a parser.
IStatusBar
The Interface for the status bar.
ITriangleCalculator
The Interface ITriangleCalculator declares the method which calculates the biggest triangle of the convex hull.
ListHull
The Class ListHull is an abstract class for a hull based on a List data structure.
MainWindow
The Class MainWindow represents the main window of the application.
MainWindowController
The controller for the main window.
ManhattanMetric
The Class ManhattanMetric implements a manhattan metric also known as taxicab geometry.
MenuAdapter
The Class MenuAdapter is a simple adapter for the MenuListener Interface.
ParserFactory
A factory for parsers.
Point
The Class Point represents a point in a cartesian coordinate system.
PointSet
The Class PointSet represents a set of points.
Quadrangle
The Class Quadrangle represents a quadrangle.
QuadranglePoint
The Enum QuadranglePoint is used to identify one of the four points of a quadrangle.
QuadrangleSequence
The Class QuadrangleSequence represents a sequence of quadrangles as used for the animation.
RandomPointsEvent
The Class RandomPointsEvent is used to describe an event invoked by user input to insert a certain number of randomly generated points into the point set.
RandomPointsEventType
The Enum RandomPointsEventType represents the type of an event which occurs when the user wants to insert 10, 50, 100, 500 oder 1000 randomly generated points into the point set.
RegExParser
A Parser which can extract a point from a string using a regular expression.
RemovePointCommand
Command for removing a point from the point set.
StatusBar
The Class StatusBar displays the current number of points in the point set, the current position of the mouse pointer over the draw panel and the coordinates of the selected point.
StatusBarController
The controller for the status bar.
TangentPair
The Class TangentPair represents a pair of tangents.
Triangle
The Class Triangle represents a triangle.
ViewEvent
An event indicating that the user has made a selection of shapes for display.
